  • Class
    Description
    AiccMetadata
    Represents metadata for an AICC eLearning module, including AICC-specific fields such as course structure, assignable units, prerequisites, objectives, credit type, time limit actions, and objective relationships.
    AiccMetadata.Builder
    Builder for constructing instances of AiccMetadata.
    AssignableUnit
    Represents an Assignable Unit (AU) in an AICC module, containing details such as the unit ID, file name, maximum score, and minimum score.
    AssignableUnitData
    Represents a collection of assignable units parsed from an AICC .au file.
    CourseData
    Represents core course data parsed from an AICC .crs file.
    CourseStructureData
    Represents the hierarchical course structure in an AICC module as parsed from a .cst file.
    CourseStructureElement
    Represents a single element within the course structure of an AICC module.
    DescriptionData
    Represents description data parsed from an AICC .des file, including the course name and description.
    ObjectiveRelationship
    Represents a relationship between two "objectives" within an AICC module.
    PrerequisiteData
    Represents prerequisite data parsed from an AICC .pre file.
